snippet: Australia are set to include Stephen O'Keefe in their squad for the third and final test against Pakistan in Sydney, putting first-choice spinner Nathan Lyon under pressure to perform ahead of the tour to India in February....
lead_paragraph: Australia are set to include Stephen O'Keefe in their squad for the third and final test against Pakistan in Sydney, putting first-choice spinner Nathan Lyon under pressure to perform ahead of the tour to India in February.

headline.main: O'Keefe to Pressure Lyon for Selection in Sydney Test
headline.print_headline: O'Keefe to Pressure Lyon for Selection in Sydney Test
